original_title: Ultimate Beginner Series: Blues Guitar with Keith Wyatt
overview: Ultimate Beginner Series - Blues Guitar with Keith Wyatt movie was released Apr 01, 2003 by the Warner Bros. studio. The continuing series of Ultimate Beginner musical instruction brings you this program that will take you to the first steps in learning to play the blues guitar. Ultimate Beginner Series - Blues Guitar with Keith Wyatt movie Instructor Keith Wyatt will teach you everything you need to know to play intros and endings, slow blues, sweet blues, and phrasing. Ultimate Beginner Series - Blues Guitar with Keith Wyatt video Includes both tablature and examples using a band that will help demonstrate the lessons.
title: Ultimate Beginner Series: Blues Guitar with Keith Wyatt
